classDiagram
    class OllamaClient {
        +str BASE_URL
        +str MODEL
        +str SYSTEM_PROMPT
        +ask_ollama(user_message: str, tools_description: str) dict
        +format_result(tool_name: str, result: str) str
        -_parse_tool_call(answer: str) dict
    }
    
    class Logger {
        +getLogger(name: str) Logger
        +error(msg: str)
    }
    
    class HTTPXClient {
        +post(url: str, json: dict, timeout: float) Response
        +raise_for_status()
    }
    
    class Response {
        +json() dict
        +raise_for_status()
    }
    
    class Environment {
        +getenv(key: str, default: str) str
    }
    
    OllamaClient --> Logger : verwendet
    OllamaClient --> HTTPXClient : verwendet für API-Calls
    OllamaClient --> Environment : liest Konfiguration
    HTTPXClient --> Response : erzeugt
    
    note for OllamaClient "Singleton-ähnliche Nutzung\nAsynchrone Methoden"
    note for OllamaClient._parse_tool_call "Privat-Methode\nExtrahiert JSON aus LLM-Antwort"